                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Du pauvre y voyant rouge, — ainsi vont nos fortunes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Sociales depuis ce cher Quatre-vingt-neuf —,",
