                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Mais j'ai tenté, pour fuir l'âpre disquiétude",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "De tous ces bruits méchants et de ce plat soleil,",
